msgid ""
"Because this is a suitable clip for :term:`hue` and the :ref:`effects-"
"hue_shift` effect:"
msgstr ""
"Perquè aquest és un clip adequat per al :term:`to<hue>` i l'efecte :ref:"
"`effects-hue_shift`:"

# skip-rule: kct-box, t-sc-box
